question: Which restaurant is available when approaching Salesforce Park Cable Car, San Francisco, CA within 190 kilometers from House of Air, San Francisco, CA?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.468617 37.804932)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.396632 37.790201)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.468617 37.804932)',4326)::geography, 190000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.468617 37.804932)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
